content.rendered:
Directed by Onir

Written by Abhishek Chatterjee

Cast Geetanjali Thapa (Archana Pradhan). Zain Khan Durrani (Alfaaz). Shray Rai Tiwari (Apu Khandelwal). Mona Ambegaonkar (Aruna Pradhan). Saheb Bhattacharjee (Partho). Chandrayee Ghosh(Priyanka). Saurav Das (Tony Baby (as Sourav Das)). Debopriya (Naren). Sahil Agarwal (Kaushal). Shefali Chauhan (Chhavi). Soumya Mukherjee (Param). Shankhu Karmakar (Lady Police). Udai Shankar (Chai Waala). Barun Chanda (Mr. Sonkar) . Parvez Patwary Milon (Raj). Moumita Pandit (Receptionist)

Languages Hindi

Producers Rahul Bhanja. Ramesh Chand. Siddharth Chauhan. Manoj Kumar. Siddharth Anand Kumar. Shoaib Lokhandwala. Vikram Mehra. Gaurav Sharma. Sahil Sharma

Production Saregama India. Yoodlee Film
